# the driver's test suite and its shared fixtures
#
# An orphan test-only module: nothing imports it, and `mach test` collects it by
# rooting at the whole source tree (as with the vector-runtime suite). It drives
# the facade build entry points and the split submodules end to end - manifest
# and dep-closure resolution, the union load walk, incremental query reuse across
# every pass, and the vector / secrecy diagnostics - over in-tree scaffolded
# project fixtures.

